Description: Computes analytical quality metrics for fitted dose-response curves
    from immunoassay data from the frequentist package curveRfreq and the Bayesian package stanassay for fitting standard curves.
URL: https://github.com/immunoplex/curveRmetrics, https://immunoplex.github.io/curveRmetrics
